div.p:
(29-30) in the glorious
Paramabhaṭṭārikāmahāvihāra founded by the mahādevī Paramabhaṭṭārikā as if she was desirous of highly
beautifying the glorious Indrapura;

The giver of land revels in heaven for sixty thousand years;
                    the one who seizes [land] as well as the one who approves (of the seizing) will
                    reside as many [years] in hell.
